snippet.title: EverQuest II Trailer
snippet.description: EverQuest II is the next generation of fantasy online gaming, a huge online world where friends come together for adventure and community.   Featuring breathtaking graphics and a vast, beautiful, and dangerous game world to explore.  EverQuest II sets the standard for graphical realism as players are immersed in the game's exciting locales and mysterious lands.
